---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Case Studies
pageDescription: "Technical case studies from Samuel Mamootil's cloud engineering career — Wipro, IBM, LTIMindtree, and NeuroSpeech. Cloud migrations, DevOps platforms, data engineering, and more."
---

<section class="section container">
  <p class="eyebrow">Selected Work</p>
  <h1>Case Studies</h1>
  <p class="lead">Each role below is presented as a case study — showing the business context, technical challenge, architecture decisions, what I owned, and what changed as a result. This is the depth behind the resume.</p>

  <div class="cs-index-grid">
    {% for cs in casestudies %}
    <a class="cs-card" href="/work/{{ cs.slug }}/">
      <div class="cs-card__header">
        <span class="cs-card__logo" style="background:{{ cs.logoColor }}">{{ cs.logoText }}</span>
        <div>
          <p class="cs-card__eyebrow">{{ cs.eyebrow }}</p>
          <h2 class="cs-card__company">{{ cs.company }}</h2>
          <p class="cs-card__role">{{ cs.role }}</p>
          <p class="cs-card__period">{{ cs.period }}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="cs-card__headline">{{ cs.headline }}</p>
      <div class="tag-list">
        {% for t in cs.tags | slice(0, 5) %}<span class="tag">{{ t }}</span>{% endfor %}
      </div>
      <span class="cs-card__cta">Read case study →</span>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">Themes across all work</p>
    <h2>What runs through everything</h2>
    <div class="skills-grid">
      <div class="skill-card">
        <h3>Cloud Platforms</h3>
        <ul class="tag-list">
          <li class="tag">AWS</li><li class="tag">Azure</li><li class="tag">GCP</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card">
        <h3>Infrastructure as Code</h3>
        <ul class="tag-list">
          <li class="tag">Terraform</li><li class="tag">Bicep</li><li class="tag">ARM Templates</li><li class="tag">CloudFormation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card">
        <h3>DevOps & CI/CD</h3>
        <ul class="tag-list">
          <li class="tag">GitHub Actions</li><li class="tag">Azure DevOps</li><li class="tag">GitLab CI/CD</li><li class="tag">Jenkins</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card">
        <h3>Containers & Orchestration</h3>
        <ul class="tag-list">
          <li class="tag">Kubernetes</li><li class="tag">Helm</li><li class="tag">Docker</li><li class="tag">EKS</li><li class="tag">ECS Fargate</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card">
        <h3>Data & AI</h3>
        <ul class="tag-list">
          <li class="tag">Redshift</li><li class="tag">AWS Glue</li><li class="tag">AWS Bedrock</li><li class="tag">SageMaker</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card">
        <h3>Governance & Security</h3>
        <ul class="tag-list">
          <li class="tag">Landing Zones</li><li class="tag">IAM</li><li class="tag">Zero Trust</li><li class="tag">Cloud Governance</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
